{"info": {"author": "Anderson R. Livramento", "author_email": "andi.devel@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.4", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6"], "description": "SimpleSMTP\n==========\n\nA very simple class to send e-mails using the Python SMTP standard lib.\n\nUsage\n-----\n\n.. code:: python\n\n    from simplesmtp import SimpleSMTP\n\n    mail = SimpleSMTP(\n        host='mail.host',\n        username='user@mail.host',\n        passw='password',\n        from_email='You <youremail@mail.host>'\n    )\n    mail.send(to_email='email@example.com', subject='Hello', email_message='World')\n\n    # Changing default from_email\n\n    mail.send(\n        from_email='Another From <email@example.com>',\n        to_email='email@example.com',\n        subject='Hello',\n        email_message='World'\n    )\n\n    # Sending to more than one recipient\n\n    mail.send(\n        to_email='email1@example.com, email2@example.com',\n        subject='Hello',\n        email_message='World'\n    )\n\n    # Attachments\n\n    mail.send(\n        to_email='email1@example.com, email2@example.com',\n        subject='Hello',\n        email_message='World',\n        attachments=[\n            {\n                'file': '/path/to/real/file',\n                'filename': 'the name that you want'\n            }\n        ]\n    )\n\n**Using SSL**\n\n.. code:: python\n\n    from simplesmtp import SimpleSMTP\n\n    mail = SimpleSMTP(\n        host='mail.host',\n        username='user@mail.host',\n        passw='password',\n        from_email='You <youremail@mail.host>',\n        port=465,\n        use_ssl=True\n    )\n    mail.send(to_email='email@example.com', subject='Hello', email_message='World')\n\n**HTML messages**\n\n.. code:: python\n\n    from simplesmtp import SimpleSMTP\n\n    mail = SimpleSMTP(\n        host='mail.host',\n        username='user@mail.host',\n        passw='password',\n        from_email='You <youremail@mail.host>'\n    )\n    mail.send(\n        to_email='email@example.com',\n        subject='Hello',\n        email_message='<html> HTML source with optional embedded images ... </html>',\n        msg_type='html'\n    )\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/andidevel/simplesmtp", "keywords": "", "license": "Apache 2.0", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "simplesmtp", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/simplesmtp/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/simplesmtp/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/andidevel/simplesmtp"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/simplesmtp/0.0.3/", "requires_dist": ["pytest ; extra == 'testing'"], "requires_python": "", "summary": "A very simple class to send e-mails using the SMTP Python Lib", "version": "0.0.3", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <p>A very simple class to send e-mails using the Python SMTP standard lib.</p>\n<div id=\"usage\">\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">simplesmtp</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">SimpleSMTP</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">SimpleSMTP</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">host</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'mail.host'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'user@mail.host'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">passw</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'password'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">from_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'You &lt;youremail@mail.host&gt;'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">send</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">to_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'email@example.com'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">subject</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">email_message</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'World'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Changing default from_email</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">send</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">from_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Another From &lt;email@example.com&gt;'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">to_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'email@example.com'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">subject</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email_message</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'World'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Sending to more than one recipient</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">send</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">to_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'email1@example.com, email2@example.com'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">subject</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email_message</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'World'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Attachments</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">send</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">to_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'email1@example.com, email2@example.com'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">subject</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email_message</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'World'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">attachments</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'file'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'/path/to/real/file'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"s1\">'filename'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'the name that you want'</span>\n        <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Using SSL</strong></p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">simplesmtp</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">SimpleSMTP</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">SimpleSMTP</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">host</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'mail.host'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'user@mail.host'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">passw</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'password'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">from_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'You &lt;youremail@mail.host&gt;'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">port</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">465</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">use_ssl</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">send</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">to_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'email@example.com'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">subject</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">email_message</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'World'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p><strong>HTML messages</strong></p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">simplesmtp</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">SimpleSMTP</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">SimpleSMTP</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">host</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'mail.host'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'user@mail.host'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">passw</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'password'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">from_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'You &lt;youremail@mail.host&gt;'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mail</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">send</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">to_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'email@example.com'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">subject</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">email_message</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'&lt;html&gt; HTML source with optional embedded images ... &lt;/html&gt;'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">msg_type</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'html'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 5344750, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "d96bbe00743cb66a767c5c14eb6bf3f5", "sha256": "b8eb59e01cffb569621a9ea98958b6812af5f5f3b8b6cfd4337d5f634c9948cf"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "simplesmtp-0.0.1-py2.py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "d96bbe00743cb66a767c5c14eb6bf3f5", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py2.py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 9756, "upload_time": "2019-02-07T00:30:52", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-02-07T00:30:52.872974Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/df/84/acf73b66eaece2db1e2abca1c6b9d200c1a6ed229b6c18343996f5779e04/simplesmtp-0.0.1-py2.py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "673c676e0f67fccfb4a6c1c853b4d9ea", "sha256": "90ce7e887d9b17cbf2b95f096904026117876f526da6de81e8c4cd89c0b3783a"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "simplesmtp-0.0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "673c676e0f67fccfb4a6c1c853b4d9ea", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 8351, "upload_time": "2019-02-07T00:30:55", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-02-07T00:30:55.060399Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/2c/20/97d8bb841c9cee83aa5a303ded723148b8f5cde1123f8c67202ae5a68285/simplesmtp-0.0.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.0.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "9188cfdb3b84e88909a1ccbad4d6f641", "sha256": "3e2a4b353cd2299d793fd0717020254044398ae8f529fd791a260f2453eb357f"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "simplesmtp-0.0.2-py2.py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "9188cfdb3b84e88909a1ccbad4d6f641", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py2.py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 10012, "upload_time": "2019-02-22T18:59:12", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-02-22T18